  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490230/extras/89598315d8291d8aad1f6e68470e60cc.avif?t=1740602618\" width=462 height=174 /></span><br><br>Manage your own saloon on the dusty roads of Desert's Edge! Wild West Saloon Simulator is an immersive Wild West saloon simulation where you can expand and upgrade your saloon with your earned fortune, take risks by betting on horse races, earn additional income through mining, and trade in the stock market. Can you become the most famous saloon owner in town, entertain your customers, and honor your grandfather's legacy? </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490230/extras/89598315d8291d8aad1f6e68470e60cc.avif?t=1740602618\" width=462 height=174 /></span><br><br>Manage your own saloon on the dusty roads of Desert's Edge! Wild West Saloon Simulator is an immersive Wild West saloon simulation where you can expand and upgrade your saloon with your earned fortune, take risks by betting on horse races, earn additional income through mining, and trade in the stock market. Can you become the most famous saloon owner in town, entertain your customers, and honor your grandfather's legacy? </p>",
